		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">- .spc file without using another program would be awesome</div>
<br />What do you mean by "another program"? The fact that it goes to another screen when playing SPCs? You can still go back by pressing Start.
<br />
<br />Or you mean that you need to use something like SPC2ROM because the PowerPak's integrated player's compability is too low? I'm sure that bunnyboy will fix that eventually. There plenty of information and code available in the posts made by blargg and myself in the thread in the Snesdev section here on the forum.

		

		</td>
